## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **pegcetacoplan Syfovre 2023** = first FDA dry AMD geographic atrophy. 수십 년간 wet AMD (anti-VEGF) 만 치료 가능했던 dry AMD GA 가 처음으로 disease-modifying 진입. C3 convertase 차단 (cross-iag). quantum-VQE 의 C3 pocket 직접 fit.
2. **avacincaptad pegol Izervay 2023** = second dry AMD GA — C5 RNA aptamer. PEG-modified oligonucleotide 가 C5 결합. RIBOZYME-axis 의 RNA aptamer modeling 직접 fit.
3. **faricimab Vabysmo 2022** = first bispecific mAb in ophthalmology (anti-VEGF-A + anti-Ang2). wet AMD + DME. WEAVE-axis bispecific scaffold 가 정확히 본 mechanism. 16-week dosing extension 임상 의미 큼.
4. **aflibercept HD 8mg Eylea HD 2023 + Susvimo port delivery 2021** = injection burden 감소 paradigm. monthly → 16-week + refillable port. sustained-release 가 ophthalmology 의 dominant trend.
5. **bimatoprost Durysta 2020 + Iluvien 2014 + Yutiq 2018 + Dextenza 2018** = sustained-release implants 폭발. anterior intracameral + posterior intravitreal + canalicular. compliance 향상.
6. **netarsudil Rhopressa 2017 + Rocklatan 2019** = first ROCK inhibitor glaucoma → first ROCK+PGF2α combo. PGF2α 단일 표적 후 처음 새 mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 ROCK pocket leverage.
7. **pilocarpine Vuity 2021 + Vizz 2023** = first FDA presbyopia drop (muscarinic miosis pinhole) → next-gen carbachol-brimonidine combo. presbyopia 가 surgical 만 가능했던 시기 종료.
8. **voretigene neparvovec Luxturna 2017** = first FDA gene therapy (RPE65 retinitis pigmentosa). subretinal AAV2 delivery. VIROCAPSID-axis 의 AAV ocular delivery direct fit. cross-pediatric_rare.
9. **teprotumumab Tepezza 2020** = IGF-1R 표적 — thyroid eye disease (Graves' ophthalmopathy). cross-endocrine. quantum-VQE 의 IGF-1R pocket leverage.
10. **dry eye 5-drug 2003-2023** = Restasis 2003 → Xiidra 2016 → Cequa 2018 → Tyrvaya 2021 → Miebo 2023. mechanism 다변화 (calcineurin → LFA-1 → nano-calcineurin → TRPM8 nasal → semifluorinated alkane evaporative). 임상 wet-lab 없음, quantum-only in-silico.

